Plot: The Nazis set up a secret base on the dark side of the moon in 1945 where they hide out and plan to return to power in 2018.
Title: Iron Sky
Actors: Julia Dietze, Christopher Kirby, Götz Otto, Udo Kier
Writer: Jarmo Puskala (original concept), Johanna Sinisalo (based on a story by), Michael Kalesniko (screenplay by), Timo Vuorensola (screenplay by)
